<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79b51d62-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s3335"><num value="3335">§ 3335.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary, for the purposes of carrying out the provisions of this subchapter, $37,500,000 for the 5-year period beginning <date date="1981-10-01">October 1, 1981</date>.</p>
